pages.privacy-policy: ExploreHorizon - Your Privacy Matters to Us Home About Travel Contacts Privacy Policy At ExploreHorizon, your privacy is our priority. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your personal information and ensure its security. By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined below. 1. Information Collection: We collect personal details such as names, contact information, and travel preferences during the booking process. Non-personal information, including browser details and IP addresses, is automatically logged for analytics and site optimization. 2. Usage of Information: Your data is used to facilitate seamless travel bookings, provide personalized recommendations, and enhance our services. Non-personal data is utilized to improve website functionality and tailor content to user preferences. 3. Data Security: We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology encrypts data transmitted between our servers and your browser. 4. Third-Party Disclosure: We do not sell, trade, or transfer your information to outside parties. However, data may be shared with trusted partners essential for trip arrangements. 5. Consent: By using our website, you consent to our Privacy Policy. Any changes will be communicated on this page. 6. pages.about: About ExploreHorizon - Crafting Unforgettable Experiences Home About Travel Contacts About Us: ExploreHorizon Welcome to ExploreHorizon, where the spirit of adventure meets unparalleled exploration. At ExploreHorizon, we are not just travel enthusiasts; we are storytellers, weaving narratives of unforgettable journeys. Our passion lies in curating unique experiences that go beyond the ordinary. From the serene landscapes of New Zealand to the cultural tapestry of Japan and the surreal beauty of Iceland, ExploreHorizon is your gateway to discovering the world's most captivating destinations. Our team comprises seasoned travelers and experts committed to crafting tailor-made adventures that resonate with your individual wanderlust. ExploreHorizon is more than a travel agency; it's a community that shares the love for exploration. Join us on a voyage of discovery, where each trip is a chapter in your personal travel story. Let ExploreHorizon be your compass to a world of wonders, creating memories that last a lifetime. Your journey begins here.
